rabbiter
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:a person employed either by a runholder, farmer, a local authority or Rabbit Board, to kill rabbits.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
